When it comes to drf application we need to follow some certain steps to handle backend and frontend
1.  **Backend** : We will use Django Rest Framework to create API endpoints. We will create models, serializers, views,url,test api at browser level
2.  **Frontend** : We will use React to create frontend application. 



Create method in serializer:
Create method in serializer it take self and validated data why the validate data this mean the serializer automatically validate the data and pass it to create method.


**validate_user means whatever the data present in serializer field will be pass to the create_super method


CreateAPIView:-It is used to create the objects in database


To send the api request to server we use  axios 


CORS(Cross Origin Resource sharing)-it's a web security feature which stops the one web from asking the data from different website without permission